        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I do some writing on the bed while Jordan sleeps. At lunch we go outside and Jordan perks up a lot. She attends a meeting and I get started on the Bovineiterology blog post. We play some Sudoku and Jordan manages another meeting before a wave of nausea arrives.",
